In the MATTER OF the Imprisonment of: Ryan Lamar PARSONS No. 320P17-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 12, 2017 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, J. Douglas Henderson, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Ryan Lamar Parsons, for Parsons, Ryan Lamar. Lorraine B. Lewis, Pro Se/Power of Attorney obo Parsons.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 11th of December 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Guilford County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 12th of December 2017."
